"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-rebecca-mcgowan-taekwondo-olympics-paris-2024-team-gb-b2583737.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The 24-year-old edged double OIympic bronze medallist Bianca Cook for a spot in Paris after a gruelling selection process  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 270, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Montgomery\", \"score\": 0.8649437357916563, \"rank\": 0.15614456442390293, \"text\": \"Bianca\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Montgomery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Montgomery\"}, {\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999985266186, \"rank\": 1.4731623823601239e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Rebecca McGowan could be forgiven for thinking she has alreadycome through her toughest testas she prepares to make her long-awaited Olympic debut in Paris next month.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9999947512179875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebecca McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999985266186, \"rank\": 1.4731623823601239e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old Scot edged double bronze medallist and three-time world championBianca Cookto the women's +73kg slot at the end of another gruelling and emotionaltaekwondoselection process.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Cook, who had set her hearton a final shot at the one major medalto still elude her, it meant heartbreak to rank alongside that of her husband, Aaron Cook, who was controversiallyoverlooked in favour of Lutalo Muhammadfor the London 2012 Games.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Livesy\", \"score\": 0.7866695677681733, \"rank\": 0.15952422835473196, \"text\": \"Aaron\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Livesy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Livesy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But McGowan's surge to prominence, which included two world medals - a bronze in 2022 in Guadalajara and silver in Baku the following year - meant that ultimately there was less cause to question the choice.\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guadalajara\", \"score\": 0.9862998294147138, \"rank\": 0.013890472410235308, \"text\": \"Guadalajara\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guadalajara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guadalajara\"}, {\"begin\": 1194, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baku\", \"score\": 0.9999997367149609, \"rank\": 2.632849470094897e-07, \"text\": \"Baku\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baku\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baku\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while McGowan is understandably wary of raking over the pair's long-standing heavyweight rivalry, she believes the high-level competition will stand her in good stead to go on and achieve something that agonisingly eluded Cook.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1298, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I overcame my biggest battle just by getting to the ParisOlympics,\\\" McGowan, who was part of the training squad that travelled to Tokyo with the team in 2021, told the PA news agency.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 1660, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9898962855706287, \"rank\": 0.010206830077974191, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had my hardest fights and I have got through them.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If we did not have that level of competition (in the GB gym) we would not have that drive and determination.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.6796871168923614, \"rank\": 0.46443906614373304, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone in the gym is constantly pushing each other to be better.\\\"\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McGowan credits her ascendancy during the abridged three-year cycle since Tokyo to the inspiration she gleaned from being up close and personal in the Japanese capital, whereCook fell to a narrow semi-final defeatand had to rouse herself to win a bronze medal for the second straight Games.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 2026, \"end\": 2031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9898962855706287, \"rank\": 0.010206830077974191, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2103, \"end\": 2111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9996483246521144, \"rank\": 0.0002906725727674821, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tokyo was a fire that was lit inside me,\\\" McGowan added.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2245, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9898962855706287, \"rank\": 0.010206830077974191, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2287, \"end\": 2294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I guess I'd accepted that it wasn't going to be my Games, but when I was out there I told myself I'd done the hard part, and I was not going to go through the same thing again in Paris.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999985266186, \"rank\": 1.4731623823601239e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had multiple injuries in this cycle, including an operation on my hip, but despite knowing how tough it was going to be to get there, I believed in myself and with the right mindset I knew I could keep striving for more.\\\"\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McGowan, who grew up in Dumbarton and is the first Scottish athlete to compete in taekwondo at the Olympics, said she had been inspired to follow in the footsteps of the domestic sport's standard bearer, Sarah Stevenson, and Serbian doubleOlympic champion Milica Mandic, whom McGowan beat to clinch her breakthrough European crown in 2021.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 3060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 2745, \"end\": 2754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dumbarton_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 2.460384038376809e-11, \"text\": \"Dumbarton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dumbarton_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dumbarton_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2772, \"end\": 2780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"score\": 0.992391785643348, \"rank\": 0.00462116617576125, \"text\": \"Scottish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2925, \"end\": 2940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Stevenson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Stevenson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Stevenson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Stevenson\"}, {\"begin\": 2946, \"end\": 2953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_language\", \"score\": 0.8468362053999323, \"rank\": 0.16459253622804154, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2977, \"end\": 2983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Milica_of_Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9999993681410337, \"rank\": 6.317985454770146e-07, \"text\": \"Milica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Milica_of_Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Milica_of_Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 2997, \"end\": 3004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have got early memories of watching Sarah then Milica winning the heavyweight title in 2012, and I watched that and thought, 'I want to be the heavyweight Olympic champion' - that's what my dream was,\\\" added McGowan, the partner of fellow GB qualifier and Tokyo silver medallist Bradly Sinden.\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah\", \"score\": 0.9996385884555625, \"rank\": 0.0003614304990637402, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah\"}, {\"begin\": 3112, \"end\": 3118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Milica_of_Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9999993681410337, \"rank\": 6.317985454770146e-07, \"text\": \"Milica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Milica_of_Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Milica_of_Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 3273, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 3321, \"end\": 3326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9898962855706287, \"rank\": 0.010206830077974191, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 3344, \"end\": 3357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradly_Sinden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bradly Sinden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradly_Sinden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradly_Sinden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have a good relationship with Milica, which is crazy - 12-year-old me would never have believed it.\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3393, \"end\": 3399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Milica_of_Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9999993681410337, \"rank\": 6.317985454770146e-07, \"text\": \"Milica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Milica_of_Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Milica_of_Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like I have been inspired by her, it's nice to inspire the younger generation in Scotland, and give them someone who has been where they are, to look up to.\\\"\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3549, \"end\": 3557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999266370573398, \"rank\": 6.054430261318716e-05, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PA  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh 